{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/introducing-else-statements","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"basic-javascript","demoType":null,"title":"Uvod u else Iskaz","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada je uslov u <code>if</code> iskazu istinit, sledeci blok koda se izvrsava. Sta se desava kada je uslov netacan? Obicno se ne desi nista. Uz <code>else</code> iskaz, moze se izvrsiti alternativni blok koda.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">if (num > 10) {\n  return \"Bigger than 10\";\n} else {\n  return \"10 or Less\";\n}\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244da","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Spojite <code>if</code> iskaze u jedan <code>if/else</code> iskaz.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18207,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/introducing-else-statements"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function testElse(val) {\n  let result = \"\";\n  // Only change code below this line\n\n  if (val > 5) {\n    result = \"Bigger than 5\";\n  }\n\n  if (val <= 5) {\n    result = \"5 or Smaller\";\n  }\n\n  // Only change code above this line\n  return result;\n}\n\ntestElse(4);","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da imate samo jedan <code>if</code> iskaz u editoru</p>","testString":"assert(__helpers.removeJSComments(code).match(/if/g).length === 1);"},{"text":"<p>Treba da koristite <code>else</code> iskaz</p>","testString":"assert(/else/g.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"},{"text":"<p><code>testElse(4)</code> treba da vrati string <code>5 or Smaller</code></p>","testString":"assert(testElse(4) === '5 or Smaller');"},{"text":"<p><code>testElse(5)</code> treba da vrati string <code>5 or Smaller</code></p>","testString":"assert(testElse(5) === '5 or Smaller');"},{"text":"<p><code>testElse(6)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Bigger than 5</code></p>","testString":"assert(testElse(6) === 'Bigger than 5');"},{"text":"<p><code>testElse(10)</code> treba da vrati string <code>Bigger than 5</code></p>","testString":"assert(testElse(10) === 'Bigger than 5');"},{"text":"<p>Ne treba da menjate kod iznad ili ispod navedenih komentara.</p>","testString":"assert(/let result = \"\";/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)) && /return result;/.test(__helpers.removeJSComments(code)));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#basic-javascript","dashedName":"introducing-else-statements","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"basic-javascript","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/introducing-else-if-statements","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/comparisons-with-the-logical-or-operator","id":"56533eb9ac21ba0edf2244da","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"function rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum) {\n  if (endNum - startNum === 0) {\n    return [startNum];\n  } else {\n    const numbers = rangeOfNumbers(startNum, endNum - 1);\n    numbers.push(endNum);\n    return numbers;\n  }\n}","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/basic-javascript/introducing-else-statements"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}